login to the system with username 'standard_user' and password 'secret_sauce'

verify the number of badge is '2'

verify 'Sauce Labs Backpack' and 'Sauce Labs Bike Light' are displayed

click on Finish button
message 'THANK YOU FOR YOUR ORDER' displays
